// - PATCH stores agent_token and git_token
// - GET returns has_git_token/has_agent_token after patching
// - Token values never returned in GET
// - Auth status returns correct status based on token_expires_at (5 states)
// - Repositories endpoint validates provider, requires git_token
// - Credential resolution merges identity + session params
